Hi,

salt-cloud currently uses version 6.5 of the Joyent API.
Joyent released version 7 on 2014-06-24.
They plan to discontinue support for 6.5 six months after that release, so on 2015-01-24.

Deprecation notice: https://apidocs.joyent.com/cloudapi/#appendix-f-sdc-65-support
Version 7 release announcement: https://www.joyent.com/company/press/joyent-smartdatacenter-7-delivers-production-ready-private-cloud-software-to-fill-growing-market-gap
